603AQG94BnMm9eE1g/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1697767565206?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=DGz1eC_m0SG3qoaf1TC9UN-owlDJCz-FSkBl5GMUijc", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "khajohn-wimolcharoesuk-703801214", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAADY5arMBjmBjDnD7wnEE3tLcTjYF2wLUFUs", "profilePic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5603AQGLqPChusH5eQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1516966617860?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=chW7hRFffD0Ivuj6lADNB1jZ4aV3Gxb8kw-uD0H7gEk", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5603AQGLqPChusH5eQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1516966617860?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=chW7hRFffD0Ivuj6lADNB1jZ4aV3Gxb8kw-uD0H7gEk", "publicIdentifier": "simon-angove-7a424b42", "recommendations/0/context": "Simon worked with Ursula but they were at different companies", "recommendations/0/date": "July 14, 2019", "recommendations/0/description": "Ursula is a representation of a dynamic, passionate and creative trainer, mentor and leader who contribute 100% expertise and professionalism in all that she is involved in. I have been fortunate enough to witness Ursula’s ability to train and develop staff & students alike, as well as maximize the skills and knowledge of those around her. Working together with Ursula for the VAVC internship program in Danang was one of my highlights. Ursula was able to provide the insight in the day to day operations during her theory lessons due to her career on the frontline, furthermore she assisted in the confidence growth of her pupils which enabled them to succeed and become the leaders they are today. The respect that myself, fellow staff, management and students have for Ursula is immense and I look forward to continuing the professional relationship moving forward.", "recommendations/0/name": "Ursula Donnellan", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Business & Quality Manager", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ursuladonnellan/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAD43MgBwFTJQ-nFOyCDF6Ewlrx2JNVfyTI", "recommendations/1/context": "Simon managed Sam directly", "recommendations/1/date": "May 10, 2012", "recommendations/1/description": "For the duration which i spent working with Sam on Hayman Island she was employed as an Senior F&B Attendant. I witnessed Sam grow and rise to be a senior staff member amongst the F&B team, more often than not taking on extra responsibility including the training and development of new staff and ensuring guest recognition. Teamwork, leadership and initiative was constantly demonstrated. Sam was a true asset to herself and to the company. Her consistency and open-minded approach to her work ensured not only her own success but also for the business. Her attention to detail and ability to follow policies and procedures is a credit to her.\nOn a personal level Sam was a pleasure to be around, her genuine gentle nature guarantee’s respect and friendship with everyone around her, as well as her great sense of humor.\nIt is with great pleasure that i write this recommendation to express my gratitude, she would be an asset company and i wish her all the best for the future.", "recommendations/1/name": "Sam Newton", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Electorate Officer, Office of the Hon David Feeney MP", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sam-newton-72145b48/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoIk0kB1YYQ_L-s1XBEPGfYQ7lXyifGRl4", "recommendations/2/context": "Simon worked with Peter  E but on different teams", "recommendations/2/date": "November 18, 2011", "recommendations/2/description": "I first met Peter upon his arrival into Danang, it didn't take Peter long to get a quality reputation and gaining alot of respect within the area for his \"Turn Around\" efforts with the Waterfront Bar & Restaurant, a largely popular expat hangout. Peter's pas