linary division was required. Mr. Razdan took immediate actions to drive the financials, operational improvements and overall upgrades to the F+B department. He also took charge the  refurbishment of the beachfront bbq restaurant and focused on other hotel departments as requested in support of my GM role. Mr. Razdan works with a high degree of passion, total professionalism, creativity and demonstrated an entrepreneurial \"Can Do\" attitude. He acted as a coach and mentor to the entire F+B team and brought a very sales-focused talent his role. You will find Mr. Razdan to be a natural hospitality leader who drives excellence from the front of house, has a high profile within the operation and enjoys regular guest contact and taking immediate action to resolve any issues that may arise. I would truly welcome the opportunity to work alongside Mr. Razdan should that opportunity ever arise and I can honestly recommend him for any GM leadership role he is keen to pursue. You will find him to be honest, transparent, professional, well versed on current hospitality trends, hotel financials and is well connected to regional TA's/Tour Operators/DMC's and related business partners. In closing, he was very well liked by senior management, hotel associates and the Vinpearl head office team. He worked well under pressure and adapted to the Vinpearl business model during his time with the company.", "recommendations/0/name": "Vinayak \"Vinny\" Razdan", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Area General Manager at FLC Hotels & Resorts", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vinayak-vinny-razdan-1307a17/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFctXQBrfqZYQyvTIcDO96MswDcmkUqhOo", "recommendations/1/context": "Michael managed Huy directly", "recommendations/1/date": "January 9, 2024", "recommendations/1/description": "Having worked with Mr Huy for one year, I can honestly recommend him as being a qualified, well rounded senior level hospitality leader. Excellent background across upscale hotel operations, works in a very transparent and ethical manner and super supportive, hands on leadership style. Knows how to achieve sales targets and analysis of financial reports. Is a creative problem solver. Well suited for Hotel GM position or Cluster role. Outstanding rooms and pre-opening background and well being closed to F&B as well.", "recommendations/1/name": "Huy Do", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Regional Director Of Operations | Cluster GM", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/huy-do-59b82960/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAzvwgcBVdGmWh2IBfK4r2LjOMxLc7ml3Pc", "recommendations/2/context": "Michael managed Jocelyn directly", "recommendations/2/date": "September 28, 2021", "recommendations/2/description": "I had the pleasure to recruit, coach and support Mr. Vaz during my assignment at Zuri Zanzibar as General Manager. His profile, background and experiences were exactly what was needed in the Operations Manager position he vary capably took responsibility for. \"Josh\" brought a cultured, well educated and hands-on leadership style to Zuri and he quickly went to work to re-build his teams which needed much training, motivation and inspiration to improve the guest experience within the Rooms Division. Josh is very much self-motivated, has the luxury background and exceptional people skills required, and balanced by solid financial awareness capabilities in managing his P+L Center. I can honestly highly recommend him as a passionate, well mannered and forward thinking Manager who conducts himself with a calm and confident nature, always with a smile and accepts direction and feedback in a respectful and positive manner. I would love to work with Josh anytime and would not hesitate to re-hire him should that opportunity ever arise. His guest contact approach is exceptional and he enjoys a high degree of visibility and resolving any issues pro-actively. Great at training as well.  ", "rec